AWSEBRDSDatabaseProperties.Description: Properties associated with the RDS database instance

AWSEBDBPassword.Description: The master password for the DB instance.

LogPublicationControl.Description: If true customer service logs will be published to S3.

XRayEnabled.Description: Enables AWS X-Ray for your environment.

AppSource.Description: The url of the application source.

ProxyServer.Description: Specifies which proxy server to be used for client connections.

AWSEBDBName.Description: The DB Name of the RDS instance

AWSEBDBUser.Description: The name of master user for the client DB Instance.
AWSEBDBUser.ConstraintDescription: must begin with a letter and contain only alphanumeric characters

InstanceType.ConstraintDescription: must be a valid EC2 instance type.

ProxyStaticFiles.Description: A mapping from virtual path to physical path.

Properties.GroupDescription: Enable database access to Beanstalk application

Metadata.ForcingMetadataUpdate: Changing something in the metadata will force re-compuation

Metadata.Description: Elastic IP Address used as entry point of Single Instance Environment
